<h3>HEADER</h3>
<p>6 size of header are allowed in the html</p> 
syntax : &lth1&gt HEADER 1 &lt/h1&gt<br />
output :  <h1> HEADER 1 </h1><br />
syntax : &lth2&gt HEADER 2 &lt/h2&gt<br />
output :  <h2> HEADER 2 </h2>
syntax : &lth3&gt HEADER 3 &lt/h3&gt<br />
output :  <h3> HEADER 3 </h3><br />
syntax : &lth4&gt HEADER 4 &lt/h4&gt<br />
output : <h4> HEADER 4 </h4><br />
syntax : &lth5&gt HEADER 5 &lt/h5&gt<br />
output : <h5> HEADER 5 </h5><br />
syntax : &lth6&gt HEADER 6 &gt/h6&lt<br />
output : <h6> HEADER 6 </h6><br />
syntax : &lth7&gt THIS LINE ACTUALLY DECLARED AS H7 HEADER BUT LOOKS LIKE SIMPLE PARAGRAPH BECAUSE H1-6 IS SUPPORTED &lt/h7&gt</br>
output : <h7> THIS LINE ACTUALLY DECLARED AS H7 HEADER BUT LOOKS LIKE SIMPLE PARAGRAPH BECAUSE H1-6 IS SUPPORTED </h7></br>

<p> HTML ignore normal line breaks and multiple spaces </p>
syntax : <br />

this is first line<br /> 
this&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbspis 2nd line<br >

output : <br />
this is first line 
this      is 2nd line

<p> line break can be added by using below syntax </p>
&ltbr&gt  :  this is not a valid line break in xhtml <br />
&lt/br&gt <br />
&ltbr /&gt : recomennded<br /><br />
syntax : <br />
&ltbr&gtline 1 &ltbr&gt line 2 &lt/br&gt line 3 &ltbr/&gt line 4 &ltbr/&gt<br />
output : <br />
<br>line 1 <br> line 2 </br> line 3 <br/> line 4 <br/>

<h3> FORMATTING on html </h3>
<h4> BOLD </h4>
tag : &ltstrong&gt word...&lt/strong&gt<br />
syntax :  This &ltstrong&gt word &lt/strong&gt is bold. <br />
output: <br/> This <strong> word </strong> is bold.<br />
<h4>ITALIC(EMPHASIS)</h4>
tag : &ltem&gt word ... &lt/em&gt<br />
syntax : This &ltem&gt word &lt/em&gt is italic.<br />
output : <br/> This <em> word </em> is italic.<br />
<h4> UNDERLINE </h4>
tag : &ltu&gt word ...&ltu&gt<br />
syntax : <br/> This &ltu&gt word &lt/u&gt is under lined.<br />
output : <br/> This <u> word </u> is under lined.
<h4>STRIKE </h4>
tag : &ltstrike&gt word ... &ltstrike&gt<br />
syntax : &ltstrike&gt This line is striked out &lt/strike&gt <br />
output : <br/> <strike> This line is striked out </strike> <br/>

<h3> UNSORTED LIST </h3>
<p>Unsorted list represented as bullet points </p>
tag : 
&ltul&gt   #unsortedlist<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt list1..&lt/li&gt   #ListItem<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt list2..&lt/li&gt  <br />
&nbsp&nbsp ....<br />
&lt/ul&gt<br />

syntax : <br />
week days &ltbr /&gt
&ltul&gt
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Sunday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Monday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Tuesday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Wednesday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Thursday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Friday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Saturday &lt/li&gt<br />
&lt/ul&gt<br />

output : <br />
week days <br />
<ul>
	<li> Sunday </li>
	<li> Monday </li>
	<li> Tuesday </li>
	<li> Wednesday </li>
	<li> Thursday </li>
	<li> Friday </li>
	<li> Saturday </li>
</ul>
 <br/>
 <h3> ORDERED LIST </h3>
 tag : 
&ltol&gt   #orderedlist<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt list1..&lt/li&gt   #ListItem<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt list2..&lt/li&gt  <br />
&nbsp&nbsp ....<br />
&lt/ol&gt<br />

syntax : <br />
week days <br />
&ltol&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Sunday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Monday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Tuesday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Wednesday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Thursday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Friday &lt/li&gt<br />
	&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&ltli&gt Saturday &lt/li&gt<br />
&lt/ol&gt<br />

output : <br />
week days <br />
<ol>
	<li> Sunday </li>
	<li> Monday </li>
	<li> Tuesday </li>
	<li> Wednesday </li>
	<li> Thursday </li>
	<li> Friday </li>
	<li> Saturday </li>
</ol>
<br /> <br />

<h3><u> IMAGE </u></h3>
tag : &ltimg src="<image source>" width="<number>" height="<number>" /&gt<br
src - source , source can be internal or external<br/>
width and height are in pixel to adjust picture size <br /><br/>

<h4> INTERNAL IMAGE </h4>
<p>Image present on local machine/server. You can give absolute path or patch from CWD </p>
syntax : &ltimg src="image/funny.jpg" /&gt<br />
output : <br/>
<img src="image/funny.jpg" /><br/>
<h4> Making some adjustment </h4>
syntax : &ltimg src="image/funny.jpg" height="100" width="100"/&gt<br/>
output :<br/>
<img src="image/funny.jpg" height="100" width="100"/>
<br/>
<h4> EXTERNAL IMAGE </h4>
<p> Image from other server. Accessed throght http </p>
syntax : &ltimg src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cf/Twelve_monkeysmp.jpg/220px-Twelve_monkeysmp.jpg" /&gt<br/>
output : <br />
<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cf/Twelve_monkeysmp.jpg/220px-Twelve_monkeysmp.jpg" /><br /><br />
